            "paragraphs": [
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "About these numbers",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "The three headline KPIs come from Locomizer's pre-extrapolated Footfall data:"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Total Footfall (Total Population) — whole population; "
                  }
                ],
                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Footfall (PaS) — mobile-holding population;"
                  }
                ],
                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Impressions (OTS) — eye contacts toward the screen."
                  }
                ],
                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "All figures use the total-audience rows (movement and visitation = All) and Locomizer's deduplicated all-day total (HOUR = 25): a visitor present for several hours is counted once, not once per hour."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Why not sum the hourly rows?",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": " Summing hours 0–23 overstates the audience by ~1.7x across these six sites (1.43x–1.94x by site), because the same person is counted in each hour they appear. HOUR = 25 is the only deduplicated figure Locomizer provides, so every KPI is built on it."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Impressions note",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "For Impressions, the all-day figure is slightly higher than the hourly sum: Locomizer derives the all-day OTS row independently, not as a sum of the 24 hours. Both come from the same eye-contacts column, so the difference is structural, not an error."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Definitions",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "HOUR = 25: all-day deduplicated row"
                  }
                ],
                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Inflation: Hourly ÷ All-day (>1 = hourly overstates)"
                  }
                ],
                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "PaS: population at screen (mobile-holding)"
                  }
                ],
                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "OTS: opportunity to see (eye contacts)"
                  }
